  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Save island from becoming a petroleum terminal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will help save Bona Island, a pristine marine life sanctuary in Panama from being devastated and converted into a petroleum terminal. CIAM will draft the legislative initiative to promote its &quot;Wildlife Refuge&quot; status. Our project will protect the numerous marine bird species, coral reef communities, sea turtles and humpback whales; but will also work to help the local communities in the area that rely on artisanal fisheries to protect their sources of livelihood.</narrative>
  </description>
